<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 03:14:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>亚洲股市下跌，日元暴跌使市场保持干预警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-27/</link><description>周四，由于对通胀的担忧，亚洲股市下跌，债券收益率飙升，而日元兑美元汇率跌破 160 美元，货币交易员准备迎接日本介入并稳定日元汇率。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 02:21:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>母公司香港交易所表示，伦敦金属交易所(LME)将香港视为全球仓库所在地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lme-eyes-hong-kong-potential-warehouse-location-hkex-ceo-says-2024-06-27/</link><description>伦敦金属交易所（LME）首席执行官周四表示，该交易所正在探索将香港列为 LME 仓库地点的可能性，因为该交易所希望加强其全球物流足迹。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 01:43:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/lme-eyes-hong-kong-potential-warehouse-location-hkex-ceo-says-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国将对进口欧盟甲苯胺启动反倾销复审</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-start-review-anti-dumping-measures-imports-eus-toluidine-2024-06-27/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，中国将对进口欧盟甲苯胺（用于染料、药品和农药）启动反倾销期终复审。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 01:31:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-start-review-anti-dumping-measures-imports-eus-toluidine-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国、日本、韩国誓言开展战略合作以促进安全和经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-japan-south-korea-vow-strategic-cooperation-boost-security-economies-2024-06-27/</link><description>美国、日本和韩国的商务和贸易部长周三誓言将在人工智能（AI）安全、出口管制、清洁能源和半导体供应链等战略问题上进行合作。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:57:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-japan-south-korea-vow-strategic-cooperation-boost-security-economies-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称，中国提供了额外的自然灾害救助资金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-provides-additional-natural-disaster-relief-funds-says-state-media-2024-06-27/</link><description>据官方媒体周四报道，中国已向几个受洪水影响的省份提供了 4.96 亿元人民币（6826 万美元）的额外自然灾害救助资金，以帮助紧急救援以及灾民的搬迁和安置。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:53:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-provides-additional-natural-disaster-relief-funds-says-state-media-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>美元坚挺，日元受创接近数十年低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/battered-yen-pinned-near-multi-decade-low-amid-resilient-dollar-2024-06-27/</link><description>周四，日元跌至 38 年低点附近，并在 1 美元兑 160 日元的弱势区间徘徊，这让市场对日本当局采取干预措施支撑日元的任何迹象保持警惕。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:30:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/battered-yen-pinned-near-multi-decade-low-amid-resilient-dollar-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：通胀恐慌和日元空头</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-26/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 21:51:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾大使没有在中国争端中寻求美国的补给支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-has-not-sought-us-resupply-support-china-dispute-ambassador-2024-06-26/</link><description>菲律宾驻华盛顿大使周三表示，在与中国在有争议的南中国海的对峙中，菲律宾尚未请求美国支持为其军队提供补给，并补充说美国只是提供援助菲律宾的“视觉”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 20:47:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-has-not-sought-us-resupply-support-china-dispute-ambassador-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，波音公司恢复向中国交付宽体飞机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-resuming-widebody-airplane-deliveries-china-source-says-2024-06-26/</link><description>据知情人士透露，波音公司正在恢复向中国供应宽体喷气式飞机，该项目最近几周因中国监管审查而暂停。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 20:24:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-resuming-widebody-airplane-deliveries-china-source-says-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>由于对中国进口产品征收更高关税，沃尔沃将推迟 EX30 在美国的发货</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-delay-ex30s-us-shipments-due-higher-tariffs-chinese-imports-bloomberg-news-2024-06-26/</link><description>沃尔沃汽车发言人周三表示，在中国出口关税上调后，沃尔沃汽车将推迟在美国交付 EX30 电动汽车，因为该公司专注于扩大中国以外紧凑型 SUV 的生产。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 19:14:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-delay-ex30s-us-shipments-due-higher-tariffs-chinese-imports-bloomberg-news-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>据《Information》报道，亚马逊将推出从中国直接发货的折扣专区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/amazon-launch-discount-section-with-direct-shipping-china-information-reports-2024-06-26/</link><description>据《The Information》周三报道，亚马逊计划在其购物网站上推出一个专区，专门销售廉价商品，这些商品可以从中国的仓库直接运送给海外消费者，并援引向中国卖家展示的幻灯片。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 17:55:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/amazon-launch-discount-section-with-direct-shipping-china-information-reports-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>秘鲁试图通过工业园激励措施吸引比亚迪汽车工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/peru-trying-lure-byd-auto-plant-with-industrial-park-incentive-2024-06-26/</link><description>秘鲁总统周三会见了中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪，邀请高管在这个安第斯国家的太平洋海岸开设商店，另一家中国公司正在那里建造一个大型港口，以促进两国之间的贸易。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 16:48:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/peru-trying-lure-byd-auto-plant-with-industrial-park-incentive-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>印度给予玉米、植物油进口关税优惠</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-allows-imports-corn-vegetable-oils-concessional-duty-2024-06-26/</link><description>印度周三在关税配额（TRQ）下允许有限进口玉米、葵花籽油、精炼菜籽油和奶粉，进口商支付零关税或较低关税，以降低食品通胀。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 15:27:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-allows-imports-corn-vegetable-oils-concessional-duty-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>德中签署数据共享声明</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germany-china-sign-declaration-data-sharing-2024-06-26/</link><description>德国一位部长周三表示，德国和中国已经签署了一份关于如何讨论跨境数据传输的意向声明，这是汽车制造商能够向德国传输数据的又一步。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 14:28:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germany-china-sign-declaration-data-sharing-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>英国人权组织发起运动阻止 Shein 潜在的伦敦首次公开募股</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-human-rights-group-launches-campaign-stop-sheins-potential-london-ipo-2024-06-26/</link><description>代表该组织的一家律师事务所周三表示，总部位于英国的人权组织“制止维吾尔族种族灭绝”已发起一项法律运动，以阻止 Shein 可能在伦敦上市，原因是对其劳工行为的担忧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 13:39:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-human-rights-group-launches-campaign-stop-sheins-potential-london-ipo-2024-06-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>